Package jellycat.flight.domain.dao

Class DaoAirplane

  • java.lang.Object
    • jellycat.flight.domain.dao.DaoAirplane
  • public class DaoAirplane
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds a collection of airplanes from airplanes described in XML Parses an XML string to read each of the airplanes and adds each valid airplane to the collection. The method uses Java DOM (Document Object Model) to convert from XML to Java primitives. Method iterates over the set of Airplane nodes in the XML string and builds an Airplane object from the XML node string and add the Airplane object instance to the Airplanes collection.

        public static Airplanes addAll​(java.lang.String xmlAirplanes)
                        throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Builds a collection of airplanes from airplanes described in XML Parses an XML string to read each of the airplanes and adds each valid airplane to the collection. The method uses Java DOM (Document Object Model) to convert from XML to Java primitives. Method iterates over the set of Airplane nodes in the XML string and builds an Airplane object from the XML node string and add the Airplane object instance to the Airplanes collection.
        Parameters:
        xmlAirplanes - XML string containing set of airplanes
        Returns:
        [possibly empty] collection of Airplanes in the xml string
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - included to keep signature consistent with other addAll methods
